These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, fanta, juice, tea, hot-chocolate
The people have 6 different hobbies: reading, magic-tricks, hiking, rock-climbing, chess, video-games
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | water  | fanta    | juice  | mirinda      | tea    |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks  | video-games | chess | reading | rock-climbing | hiking |

