.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: martial-arts, epic, animation, adventure, thriller, musical
6 different pets are kept: ferret, rat, hamster, fish, horse, hedgehog
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
5. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
6. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
7. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
9. the person watching martial-arts movies is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | thriller | epic | musical | adventure     | animation  |
| Pet           | hamster | rat    | ferret      | hedgehog  | fish | horse |

