.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: funk, jazz, trance, metal, disco, r&b
There are 6 different nationalities: dutch, italian, malaysian, spanish, pakistani, egyptian
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the spanish is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of metal##1
4. the fan of trance is on the right of the pakistani##1
5. the fan of disco is on the right of the egyptian##1
6. the fan of disco is on the left of the italian##1
7. the spanish is on the far right##1
8. the malaysian is the fan of metal##1
9. the fan of trance is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | r&b   | disco      | jazz | funk  | trance   |
| Nationality   | malaysian | egyptian | dutch | italian   | pakistani | spanish |

