.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: salsa, metal, hip-hop, r&b, house, techno
The people use 6 different means of transport: subway, roller, motorbike, trike, skateboard, car
1. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the car##1
4. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of house##1
5. the person driving the car is the fan of r&b##1
6. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
7. the fan of house is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | r&b | salsa      | metal  | techno | house |
| Transport     | subway | car  | skateboard | motorbike | trike  | roller    |

