.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: video-games, board-games, skydiving, dancing, drawing, camping
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, gospel, hip-hop, punk, indie
 1. the fan of gospel is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 3. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 5. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 6. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | dancing | camping | video-games | drawing | board-games | skydiving  |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | hip-hop  | gospel  | dubstep | punk      | blues |

