4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the owner of the cat is the person driving the scooter##1
6. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the train##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
8. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
