.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: trance, folk, metal, blues, d&b, house
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skiing, cycling, soccer, baseball, sailing, rowing
1. the fan of metal is the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is the fan of blues##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is the fan of house##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
7. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of house##1
8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Music-Genre   | house | trance  | d&b     | metal    | folk  | blues          |
| Sport         | cycling  | skiing | soccer | sailing | baseball | rowing |

