.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-9::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, cola, coffee, fanta, lemonade
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, tram, car, airplane, scooter
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Beverage    | fanta | 7up | coffee | lemonade    | milk | cola      |
| Transport   | tram   | boat     | helicopter      | airplane | scooter           | car |

