.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: potato, cucumber, carrot, strawberry, zucchini, garlic
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: superhero, romance, sports, fantasy, comedy, scientific
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
3. the person watching romance movies is the person eating cucumber##1
4. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
7. the person eating garlic is the person watching superhero movies##1
8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
9. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cucumber | garlic   | zucchini  | carrot    | strawberry  | potato |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | superhero | scientific | comedy | sports | fantasy |

