.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people have 6 different jobs:  musician, firefighter, journalist, police-officer, electrician, security-guard
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the musician is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
4. the journalist is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the firefighter is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking water is the police-officer##1
8. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the electrician is on the left of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage   | coffee    | water     | cola | soy-milk | fanta | hot-chocolate   |
| Job        | security-guard | police-officer | electrician | journalist   | musician    | firefighter |

