5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
6. the german is on the left of the pakistani##1
7. the mexican is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the german##1
9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | german | pakistani    | russian | mexican  | japanese |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | car | roller | quad-bike   | ship | boat    |

