.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-17::.
6 different pets are kept: rabbit, dog, fish, chinchilla, horse, mouse
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, sailing, ice-hockey, snowboarding, soccer
1. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |    3     |    4     |    5    |       6       |
| Pet     | horse  | chinchilla       | mouse   | rabbit      | fish | dog          |
| Sport   | snowboarding | basketball | sailing | biathlon | ice-hockey | soccer |

